6. Access, modify, delete, download, transfer your personal information
After you complete the account registration of the software, you can access, modify, delete, download and transfer the personal information you submit to us at any time. You may request us to delete personal information in the following circumstances
1)
If our handling of personal information violates laws and regulations
2)
If our handling of personal information violates our agreement with you
3)
If we terminate the operation and service of the software
If we decide to respond to your deletion request, we will also try our best to notify third parties who have obtained your personal information from us and require them to delete it in a timely manner, unless otherwise provided by laws and regulations or these third parties have obtained your independent authorization. For personal information that is difficult to access, modify, or delete directly on the client, you can also submit relevant applications to us through the contact information provided in this policy